00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:27,242
you're going to be eating out on that game for the rest of your life.

563
00:28:27,282 --> 00:28:30,003
That's, I'm going to be in this business for a long time money.

564
00:28:31,004 --> 00:28:34,286
But it's not, it's still, I have to work for a living money.

565
00:28:34,506 --> 00:28:39,209
And by the way, before I, before I leave this slide, I want to, I beg you,

566
00:28:39,689 --> 00:28:42,411
please, please support bigcatclipart.com.

567
00:28:44,321 --> 00:28:45,522
And the good work they do.

