00:30:59,249 --> 00:31:00,430
I'll be straightforward about that.

615
00:31:00,690 --> 00:31:01,750
Bear in mind, I still get abuse.

616
00:31:02,050 --> 00:31:04,651
I have gotten some input from out in the wild that

