00:31:52,555 --> 00:31:56,057
If someone is on the forums and you can see that they're just there to cause trouble,

637
00:31:56,617 --> 00:31:57,297
ban them.

638
00:31:58,578 --> 00:31:59,699
If people are making a noise,

